About genetic algorithm (GA) and neural networks (NN) - my suggestion is in using GA without NN to solve travelling salesman problem (TSP). I don't think that training of deep neural networks (DNNs) with GA is a good idea. I tried to do it several years ago and this even works for small NNs, but it's not such efficient as other learning approaches for DNNs
